    ("LOC_BUILDING_SANCTUARY_NAME",                               "Environmental Conservation Department"),
    ("LOC_BUILDING_SANCTUARY_DESCRIPTION",                        "Upon completion, it will cause the population of one randomly Biological Resource on features in this city to expand nearby. [NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Rainforest, Marsh and Floodplains tiles in this city grant +1 Appeal to adjacent tiles. [NEWLINE][NEWLINE]+1 [ICON_FOOD] Food to all Feature tiles in this city; extra +1 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production if with any resource; extra +3 [ICON_GOLD] Gold if with Charming appeal; extra +1 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture if with Breathtaking appeal. [NEWLINE]+2 [ICON_FOOD] Food, +2 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture and +6 [ICON_GOLD] Gold Natural Wonder tiles in this city."),
